WEBVTT

00:03:59.848 --> 00:04:02.681
and renders human life worthless.

00:04:04.509 --> 00:04:06.570
When young men are willing

00:04:07.418 --> 00:04:08.908
to join gangs

00:04:10.043 --> 00:04:12.682
and brutalize their communities

00:04:12.706 --> 00:04:13.978
for a small fee,

00:04:15.382 --> 00:04:17.743
and women are raped on the way to work,

00:04:17.767 --> 00:04:19.763
and, when they report this,

00:04:19.787 --> 00:04:22.670
the perpetrators bribe
their way out of jail,

00:04:23.521 --> 00:04:26.194
and when young girls
have to sell their bodies

00:04:27.270 --> 00:04:29.116
to buy sanitary towels,